      "name": "Prandtl Number",
      "formula": "Pr = ν/α = (μ * cp)/k",
      "description": "Dimensionless number representing the ratio of momentum diffusivity to thermal diffusivity",
      "usage_context": "Used to characterize relative thickness of velocity and thermal boundary layers",
